Henry Vogel https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Henry_Vogel 0 Vogel is the German and Dutch word for "bird", while in Albanian it is the word for “small”. Alternate spelling is Fogel. Vogel is also a surname originating in German and Dutch-speaking countries. Equivalent surnames are Bird or Byrd in English or L'Oiseau in French. Notable people with the surname include: Vogel is the_German_and_Dutch_word for " bird " , while in Albanian_it is the_word for “_small_” . Alternate_spelling is Fogel .
